pology of common annotator errors is\nextracted. Finally, we provide baseline models for all stages of the\nfact-checking pipeline and publish the NLI datasets, as well as our annotation\nplatform and other experimental data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 Jan 2022 18:48:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 31 Jan 2022 19:49:12 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 17 Oct 2022 10:00:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-12"}
