tial of this substation-based CSP is demonstrated for a\nwide variety of crystal systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 Jan 2022 21:06:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 31 May 2022 15:03:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-01"}
