 model with fitted\ncoefficients that describes the evolution of the velocity and radius. Finally,\nwe compare the lengths of the stagnated streamers with predictions based on the\nconventional stability field.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Jan 2022 01:16:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-13"}
