culiar stars. The light emission\ncontributes to the light variability only if a significant fraction of light is\nabsorbed in the magnetosphere.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Jan 2022 10:46:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-14"}
