ating and more confidently disfavour exotic\nmodels with high Lyman-$\\alpha$ fluxes, low X-ray efficiencies and high radio\nproduction efficiencies in early galaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Jan 2022 14:11:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 20 May 2022 12:28:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-23"}
