ical consistency\nof the generator to make predictions on the stationary state of the subsystem\ndynamics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Jan 2022 15:53:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 25 Jul 2022 10:46:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-10"}
