volutions over multiple timescales, with separate processes modulating a\nseizure state's occurrence and duration. These findings provide new insight\ninto the patterns and mechanisms of intra-patient seizure variability, with\npotential implications for forecasting and treating seizures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Jan 2022 15:59:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-28"}
